              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/42349529/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3424290/" class=" " title="Chloe Chang">Chloe Chang</a>
                (低着头往前跑的人。)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="42349529">
